name: Hotel-management-system
tagline: This is a hotel management system I made as a school project in 2014
body:
### Authors and Contributors If you wish to better this, go right ahead, I would love to see what this can develop into :D ### Support or Contact If you wish to use this but don't know what's what, drop me a line, I'm more than willing to help with anything.
P.S. If you are intending on making money from this, I would appreciate a heads up and consideration ;D
